Package com.utils

package com.utils
This package includes utility classes for working with DB and one Enum class.

Classes in package:

  • UserRole - Enum class presents a user roles
  • PropertiesManager - Utility class for working with DB properties
  • ConnectionPoolManager - Utility class for working with DB connections

Since:
1.0
  • Class
    Description
    ConnectionPoolManager
    The ConnectionPoolManager class is a utility class for managing a connection pool.
    PropertiesManager
    The PropertiesManager class is a utility class for managing properties loaded from "application.properties" file.
    UserRole
    The UserRole enum class represents the roles of users, which can be either "User" or "Admin".
